at the factory that badly?

7
00:00:55,110 --> 00:00:56,520
If you work there like me,

8
00:00:57,470 --> 00:00:58,840
and the only thing clean

9
00:00:58,840 --> 00:01:00,280
about you will be your teeth.

10
00:01:07,230 --> 00:01:08,790
What's so good about working there?

11
00:01:09,920 --> 00:01:11,920
Once you leave home
and enter the factory gates,

12
00:01:12,590 --> 00:01:14,680
you'll never see a ray of light again.

13
00:01:15,280 --> 00:01:16,920
You look up, and all you see is gray.

14
00:01:18,870 --> 00:01:20,430
Then, why are you working there?

15
00:01:23,870 --> 00:01:25,710
We only need one man in our family

16
00:01:28,510 --> 00:01:29,710
