17
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:36,350
Have you thought about the future?

18
00:01:37,590 --> 00:01:38,640
The future?

19
00:01:39,710 --> 00:01:42,350
Have you thought about
what you'll be like in ten years?

20
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:50,790
What's the point?

21
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:53,870
I just care about tomorrow.

22
00:01:54,800 --> 00:01:56,730
All's well as long as the sun
comes out tomorrow.

23
