26
00:02:56,190 --> 00:02:57,430
Why the feast?

27
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,280
Are our troubles over?

28
00:03:00,870 --> 00:03:01,750
I don't want you

29
00:03:01,750 --> 00:03:03,150
to live like this anymore,

30
00:03:03,150 --> 00:03:05,470
hiding and struggling.

31
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,590
It's all my fault.

32
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:09,560
I let you both down.

33
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:11,590
We're doing fine, aren't we?

34
00:03:11,590 --> 00:03:13,120
We can still have grilled meat.

35
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:23,420
Dad?

36
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:24,430
Why are you crying?

37
00:03:26,470 --> 00:03:28,000
The smoke got into my eyes.

38
00:03:35,840 --> 00:03:36,960
This smells great.

39
00:03:44,640 --> 00:03:45,870
Chunsheng, eat while it's hot.

40
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,310
Chunsheng! Why did you do that?

41
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,080
Dad.

42
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:57,030
We can't just give up.

43
00:03:57,710 --> 00:03:59,280
We'll get the money back

44
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:01,080
and we'll explain everything
to everyone!

45
00:04:03,470 --> 00:04:04,310
Dad!

