from the city's investment office.

64
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:55,120
I can do that.

65
00:06:55,120 --> 00:06:56,270
No problem.

66
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,190
Good.

67
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,120
I have matters to attend to.

68
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:01,070
I'll let you get busy.

69
00:07:02,510 --> 00:07:04,750
