72
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:09,950
He likes chess.

73
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:32,720
You know this place well.

74
00:07:32,730 --> 00:07:34,430
You order and I'll pay.

75
00:07:40,830 --> 00:07:43,000
Two of your most expensive steaks.

76
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:43,870
All right.

77
00:07:49,210 --> 00:07:50,430
What are you trying to do here?

78
00:07:50,430 --> 00:07:51,510
Eat.

79
00:07:53,070 --> 00:07:55,120
I want to know
what this fancy western steak

80
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:56,310
