81
00:07:59,310 --> 00:08:02,120
After this, we'll go to the civil affairs
office and get divorced.

82
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:03,390
You can go abroad.

83
00:08:05,070 --> 00:08:06,270
For real this time.

84
00:08:08,430 --> 00:08:09,630
