Li.

214
00:18:40,240 --> 00:18:41,350
Xia Yu, you're here.

215
00:18:41,350 --> 00:18:42,480
You're finally off the clock.

216
00:18:43,510 --> 00:18:44,550
Here you go, Xia Yu.

217
00:18:45,240 --> 00:18:46,550
You must be exhausted lately.

218
00:18:47,790 --> 00:18:49,160
Just hang in there a little longer.

219
00:18:49,160 --> 00:18:51,850
Once we ship this batch of goods,
the factory will be back on track.

220
00:18:52,030 --> 00:18:53,510
I'm fine, Li. I can manage.

221
00:18:54,000 --> 00:18:55,310
You've got the night shift tomorrow.

222
00:18:55,310 --> 00:18:57,070
- Yes?
- Go home and get some sleep.

223
00:18:58,000 --> 00:18:59,590
Xia Yu, it's for you.

224
00:19:02,070 --> 00:19:02,910
Hello?

225
00:19:05,960 --> 00:19:07,750
All right. I'll see you later.

226
00:19:14,270 --> 00:19:15,510
Sweet melon.

227
00:19:16,200 --> 00:19:17,270
That girl...

228
00:19:18,270 --> 00:19:19,790
Has a date.

229
00:20:02,270 --> 00:20:03,200
Xiasheng!

230
00:20:24,510 --> 00:20:25,750
It looks great on you.

231
00:20:27,240 --> 00:20:28,920
Who dresses like this?

232
00:20:29,550 --> 00:20:31,590
This is how we dress back home.

233
00:20:34,230 --> 00:20:35,120
What's this?

234
00:20:35,240 --> 00:20:36,270
It's for you.

235
00:20:37,350 --> 00:20:38,550
I don't need it.

236
00:20:39,310 --> 00:20:41,960
You didn't need it before you knew me.

237
00:20:42,510 --> 00:20:44,000
But now you do.

238
00:20:45,510 --> 00:20:46,550
Just take it.

239
00:20:50,310 --> 00:20:51,200
Come on.

240
00:20:51,450 --> 00:20:53,000
I didn't take you out to sea last time.

241
00:20:53,000 --> 00:20:54,270
I'll make it up to you.

242
00:21:12,510 --> 00:21:14,480
Faster!

243
00:21:42,200 --> 00:21:43,350
The weather's nice.

244
00:21:52,310 --> 00:21:53,240
Xia Yu.

245
00:21:54,920 --> 00:21:56,720
Choose your words carefully.

246
00:21:56,720 --> 00:21:58,480
You only have one chance to explain.

247
00:22:07,590 --> 00:22:09,270
I didn't mean to hide it from you.

248
00:22:11,720 --> 00:22:12,790
My dad

249
00:22:13,750 --> 00:22:15,160
used to run a factory.

250
00:22:16,590 --> 00:22:18,160
The business was struggling.

251
00:22:19,680 --> 00:22:20,830
He tried to save it,

252
00:22:21,680 --> 00:22:23,070
but he got scammed.

253
00:22:26,440 --> 00:22:28,000
The factory was taken from him.

254
00:22:29,270 --> 00:22:30,750
My brother and I tracked the guy down

255
00:22:31,440 --> 00:22:33,030
and beat him up pretty bad.

256
00:22:35,680 --> 00:22:37,200
We thought we killed him,

257
00:22:39,510 --> 00:22:41,070
so we ran.

258
00:22:43,240 --> 00:22:44,680
That day when I saw the police,

259
00:22:46,270 --> 00:22:48,000
