262
00:23:02,550 --> 00:23:04,200
I have no idea where he is now.

263
00:23:06,070 --> 00:23:07,680
He's probably somewhere

264
00:23:07,680 --> 00:23:09,510
no one can find him.

265
00:23:19,510 --> 00:23:20,510
You know what?

266
00:23:21,830 --> 00:23:23,990
I'm making pretty good money
from this shipping job.

267
00:23:25,270 --> 00:23:26,510
So what are you planning to do?

268
00:23:28,030 --> 00:23:29,550
I want to go back home.

269
00:23:31,920 --> 00:23:33,350
You should.

270
00:23:40,240 --> 00:23:41,830
Would you come with me?

271
00:23:47,070 --> 00:23:48,350
Why?

272
00:23:51,510 --> 00:23:53,480
It's not like you're not coming back,

273
00:23:55,750 --> 00:23:56,590
right?

274
00:24:01,510 --> 00:24:03,240
I might not.

275
00:24:14,750 --> 00:24:15,750
It's nice here.

276
00:24:16,510 --> 00:24:17,830
You're doing well here.

277
00:24:19,070 --> 00:24:20,590
You shouldn't leave with me.

278
00:24:26,510 --> 00:24:27,440
It's nice here.

279
00:24:37,540 --> 00:24:44,540
(Qianzimeng Garment Factory)

280
00:24:54,480 --> 00:24:55,920
